#: weblate/static/loader-bootstrap.js:1989
msgid "Weblate is now scanning the repository, please be patient."
msgstr "Weblate ກຳລັງສະແກນ Repository, ກະລຸນາລໍຖ້າ."

#: weblate/static/loader-bootstrap.js:2176
msgid ""
"Notification settings removed, please do not forget to save the changes."
msgstr "ການຕັ້ງຄ່າການແຈ້ງເຕືອນຖືກລຶບແລ້ວ, ກະລຸນາຢ່າລືມບັນທຶກການປ່ຽນແປງ."

#: weblate/static/loader-bootstrap.js:2448
msgctxt "Alert to user when opening browser developer console"
msgid "Stop!"
msgstr "ຢຸດ!"

#: weblate/static/loader-bootstrap.js:2454
msgid ""
"This is a browser feature intended for developers. If someone told you to "
"copy-paste something here, they are likely trying to compromise your Weblate "
"account."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ແມ່ນຄຸນສົມບັດຂອງບຣາວເຊີສຳລັບນັກພັດທະນາ. ຖ້າມີຄົນບອກໃຫ້ທ່ານຄັດລອກ-ວາງບາງຢ່າງທີ່ນີ້, "
"ພວກເຂົາອາດກຳລັງພະຍາຍາມແຮັກບັນຊີ Weblate ຂອງທ່ານ."

#: weblate/static/loader-bootstrap.js:2460
msgid "See https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Self-XSS for more information."
msgstr "ເບິ່ງ https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Self-XSS ສຳລັບຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມ."

